  Alan Grayson and his wife Lolita Grayson have agreed to annul their 24-year marriage in Florida on Tuesday . 
  The couple had accused each other of bigamy, financial abandonment and battery . 
  Mrs Grayson was married to another man when they wed in 1990 . 
  She had claimed in court papers that she was divorced from her first husband when she married the congressman . 
  They are still in talks on a settlement . 
 